                     <interp inst="t17970426-73-punish410" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970426-73-defend600 t17970426-73-punish410"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron HOTHAM.</p>
